{"tid":494660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【生意急升】明星效應潮興漂白肛門 「伴侶要求學AV女優」","createTime":"2017-12-10T00:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T00:55:15.000Z","uid":13468,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4bbf16c25055ddff774d49f44b4f58a058eadb77","tid":494660,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:21:56.000Z","msg":"【生意急升】明星效應潮興漂白肛門 「伴侶要求學AV女優」<br />\n<br />\n早前外國有女星在真人騷公開示範「肛門漂白」的美容方法，在明星效應的刺激下，不少女性甚至男性都追潮流進行漂白，倫敦一間著名美容診所表示，在過去一年生意額上升了23%。<br />\n<br />\n今年4月Marnie Simpson及Sophie Kasaei在真人騷《Geordie Shore》中示範漂白肛門，據悉Charlotte Crosby及Kourtney Kardashian等名人亦曾「肛門漂白」，令這種美容方法開始受人矚目。倫敦一間著名美容診所發言人稱，過去一年生意額上升了23%，而且除了女性外，亦有小部分男顧客上門。<br />\n<br />\n肛門漂白是將肛門附近皮膚顏色變淺，藉此與身體其他部位的顏色更接近，診所發言人說﹕「我相信女顧客（光顧）因受到伴侶的壓力，要求模仿AV片中的女優。」而且顧客年齡層極廣，並不局限年輕或年長女性。<br />\n<br />\n「肛門漂白」分激光或塗藥膏兩種方式，其中95%顧客選擇激光，5%選擇用藥膏。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171208/57547632\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57547632&d=N77O3Tm2IL4Pz41%2FRoyO27%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f3e3acc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57547632&h=5f54d45f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171208/57547632</a>"},{"pid":"c994be537ebe8b431e6ad78a8e957defb9ca0c1e","tid":494660,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:25:29.000Z","msg":"有冇得漂pink lin?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2549b42de1ba2a3b62df20910ce85dfe873e3989","tid":494660,"uid":84228,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:38:26.000Z","msg":"黑鮑會唔會已經做左？"},{"pid":"27f2343b5cbe67178eb664d8fab1ba58c80b5937","tid":494660,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:42:17.000Z","msg":"倫敦一間著名美容診所發言人稱，過去一年生意額上升了23%，而且除了女性外，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亦有小部分男顧客上門。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6362028678a8f172e15cc924f6ed0d65c556c672","tid":494660,"uid":3571,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:50:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd84495e583632b45e879a8fe1946442edde5f90","tid":494660,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}